v0.0.2 Jun 26, 2019
====================

* Refactor layers
  - composer modules are now installed into their own layer
  - global modules moved to packages layer
  - symlink app/vendor dir into packages layer
  - updated libcfbuildpack
  - updated layer flags to allow optimized builds
  (https://www.pivotaltracker.com/story/show/162492533)

* Run 'composer global require' for all packages set in buildpack.yml

* Add support for composer to use github token
  - Moved github token from yml to env
  - Validate token and check rate limits
  (https://www.pivotaltracker.com/story/show/162492533)

* Add composer 1.8.6
  for stack(s) org.cloudfoundry.stacks.cflinuxfs2, org.cloudfoundry.stacks.cflinuxfs3, io.buildpacks.stacks.bionic
  (https://www.pivotaltracker.com/story/show/166609732)


